<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Sedan:ital@0;1&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link
        href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Platypi:ital,wght@0,300..800;1,300..800&family=Sedan:ital@0;1&family=Trade+Winds&display=swap"
        rel="stylesheet">
    <title>Shruti-Sangam Tabla Courses</title>
    <style>
        * {
            font-family: "Sedan", serif;
        }

        header {
            position: relative;
        }

        .info-box:hover {
            transform: scale(1);
        }

        ul {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: rgb(32, 6, 57)
        }

        .btn:hover {
            transform: scale(1.1);
            transition: 1s;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    {{>header}}
    <section>
        <div class="sec-div bg-white rounded-4" style="padding-bottom:80px;">
            <div>
                <h1 class="text-center py-5 fw-bold text-dark text-decoration-underline head">Tabla Courses</h1>
            </div>
            <div class="d-flex justify-content-center" style="padding-bottom:20px;">
                <div class="info-box shadow-lg w-50">
                    <h3 class="text-center p-2 rounded-2 bg-warning">Beginner</h3>
                    <div class="pt-4">
                        <h4 style="color:darkblue">Tabla Course part 1</h4>
                        <p>In this course, the student learns finger techniques, basic rhythm patterns and hand
                            positioning, contemporary rhythms, folk rhythms and builds coordination and technical
                            skills.
                        </p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Course-Duration: 6-8 months</li>
                            <li>Certification Included</li>
                            <li>Masterclass Included</li>
                        </ul>
                        <h5 class="fw-bold">INR 400/Session</h5>
                        <p>Per Session(30 Min Each)</p>
                        <button class="btn btn-warning"><a class="text-decoration-none text-dark"
                                href="/tablaBeginner">See
                                Course</a></button>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="info-box shadow-lg w-50">
                    <h3 class="text-center p-2 rounded-2 bg-warning">Intermediate</h3>
                    <div class="pt-4">
                        <h4 style="color:darkblue">Tabla Course part 2</h4>
                        <p>Students who are ready to master different taals. In this course, the student learns about
                            different gharanas of tabla and focuses on building technique, rhythm, coordination and
                            musical understanding.</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Course-Duration: 8-10 months</li>
                            <li>Certification Included</li>
                            <li>Masterclass Included</li>
                        </ul>
                        <h5 class="fw-bold">INR 600/Session</h5>
                        <p>Per Session(60 Min Each)</p>
                        <button class="btn btn-warning"><a class="text-decoration-none text-dark" href="/tablaCourseInt">See
                                Course</a></button>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="info-box shadow-lg w-50">
                    <h3 class="text-center p-2 rounded-2 bg-warning">Advance</h3>
                    <div class="pt-4">
                        <h4 style="color:darkblue">Tabla Course Part 3</h4>
                        <p>Through this course, the Tabla player gains the confidence and ability to express themselves
                            through music in front of an audience and take their love of Tabla to new heights. The
                            student learns advanced level compositions and a solo Tabla arrangement in this course.</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Course-Duration: 10-12 months</li>
                            <li>Certification Included</li>
                            <li>Masterclass Included</li>
                        </ul>
                        <h5 class="fw-bold">INR 800/Session</h5>
                        <p>Per Session(60 Min Each)</p>
                        <button class="btn btn-warning"><a class="text-decoration-none text-dark" href="/flute">See
                                Course</a></button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    {{>footer}}
    <script src="/js/script.js"></script>
</body>

</html>